/******************************************************************************                      
** Name		 : USP_PV_GetPendingGiftAddition                      
** Short Desc: Get pending gift additions for given valuation ids. This excludes    
** the reconcilled and discarded transaction                         
** Full Description: Get pending gift additions for given valuation ids. This excludes    
** the reconcilled and discarded transaction
**                              
** Input Arguments:   	@EventID INT
**	,@ReturnStatus INT  OUTPUT
**	,@ErrorDesc VARCHAR(8000) OUTPUT             
** Sample Call     
         
 EXEC dbo.USP_PV_GetPendingGiftAddition @XMLValuation = '<ValuationCollection>  
      <InsertList>  
      <Valuation ValuationID="156" />   
      </InsertList>  
      </ValuationCollection>'
**             
**                      
**                      
** Standard declarations                      
**       SET LOCK_TIMEOUT         30000   -- 30 seconds                      
**                       
** Created By: Mohamed Salih 
** Company   : Kaspick & Company                      
** Project   : BackOffice Integration                      
** Created DT: 17-Mar-14               
